A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Task Force on Education Funding and Student Population Growth
3 FOR the purpose of establishing the Task Force on Education Funding and Student
4 Population Growth; and generally relating to the Task Force on Education Funding
5 and Student Population Growth.
6 SECTION 1. BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF MARYLAND,
7 That:
8 (a) There is a Task Force on Education Funding and Student Population Growth.
9 (b) The Task Force consists of the following members:
10 (1) one member of the Senate of Maryland, appointed by the President of
11 the Senate;
12 (2) one member of the House of Delegates, appointed by the Speaker of the
13 House; and
14 (3) the following members, appointed by the Governor:
15 (i) one representative of the State Department of Education;
16 (ii) one representative of the Maryland Association of Boards of
17 Education;
18 (iii) one representative of the Maryland State Education Association;
19 (iv) one representative of Maryland Free State PTA;
